   Now Sing Along:
   O Solstice Tree,
   O Solstice Tree...
   ---
   All Sorts of People Celebrate
   This Special Winter Day;
   Even Santa Shows Up
   ----
   By Suzanne Alexander
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/23/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A1
</SO>
